Package: Fonology
Type: Package
Title: Functions for segmental phonology
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Guilherme Duarte Garcia
Maintainer: Guilherme Duarte Garcia <guilherme.garcia@lli.ulaval.ca>
Description: The package currently contains functions to determine minimal matrices 
    of distinctive features and to plot vowel trapezoids given a specific language
    using ggplot2 as well as the vowel package in LaTeX.
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
